file.name: components.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  version: 0.0.1
  title: '@viron/lib components'

components:
  schemas:
    VironPager:
      type: object
      properties:
        maxPage:
          type: integer
        currentPage:
          type: integer
      required:
        - maxPage
        - currentPage

    VironCreatedAt:
      description: 作成日時
      type: string
      format: date-time

    VironUpdatedAt:
      description: 更新日時
      type: string
      format: date-time

  responses:
    VironXEnumResponse:
      description: x-enumに指定されたオペレーションのレスポンス定義
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string

  parameters:
    VironIdPathParam:
      name: id
      in: path
      schema:
        type: string
      required: true

    VironPagerSizeQueryParam:
      name: size
      in: query
      description: Size of list
      schema:
        type: integer
      required: false

    VironPagerPageQueryParam:
      name: page
      in: query
      description: Page number of list
      schema:
        type: integer
      required: false

    VironSortQueryParam:
      name: sort
      in: query
      description: Sort specification of list
      schema:
        type: array
        minItems: 1
        items:
          type: string
          pattern: '^.+?:(asc|desc)$'
      style: form
      explode: false

    VironIdQueryParam:
      name: id
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false

    VironRoleIdQueryParam:
      name: roleId
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false

    VironEmailQueryParam:
      name: email
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false
